05:57.470 --> 06:01.700
Another point and this is a very important one is be positive.

06:01.760 --> 06:06.900
You have to realize that negotiating doesn't mean being mean.

06:07.130 --> 06:08.490
It's the exact opposite.

06:08.540 --> 06:16.850
You want to explore the situations that are available to you and negotiations are a win win situation.

06:16.910 --> 06:21.410
If you go into a negotiation thinking that you have to screw over the other person or there's always

06:21.410 --> 06:26.850
one person that went to one person that loses that's not a good way to negotiate.

06:27.960 --> 06:36.270
Negotiation is finding a balance between what two people what and then finally when negotiating you

