have to have stakes What does that mean.

06:39.720 --> 06:46.380
No that doesn't mean delicious meat steaks means you have to have something on the line.

06:46.380 --> 06:53.360
If there's no risk and you knew for sure that the other side would sign a contract or accept the salary.

06:53.700 --> 07:00.300
Then what incentive did they have to offer you more if they know that you're desperate and this is the

07:00.300 --> 07:06.050
only job that you can get while there's zero chance of you negotiating with them.

07:06.120 --> 07:13.270
Your alternatives is what stakes are by showing companies that you have other options.

07:13.270 --> 07:17.600
Maybe you have multiple offers or another company that wants to hire you.

07:17.650 --> 07:23.650
You allow the person across the table who's negotiating with you to know that you're willing to walk

07:23.650 --> 07:25.750
away from the table without a deal.

07:26.050 --> 07:29.600
